4 Sections 2001.2, 2006, and 2013 of this title,
5 determine the interest rates on loans and the maximum
6 amount that may be loaned with and without security to
7 any member, and determine the rate of interest refund,
8 if any, to be made to members.
9 A majority of the board may, however, agree to exclude
10 loans made at rates of interest lower than the basic rate
